name: Strange Attractor
description: A series of contemplative creations, inviting the viewer to dive into an ever evolving murmuration. Inspired by the movements of nature, Strange Attractor is also a tribute to the powerful energy emerging from Chinese and Japanese calligraphy. When complex equations and randomness draw an endless choreography... This real-time generative art experiment was created by mixing an homemade GLSL trail system with curl noise and strange attractor (dadras equations). 1080x1080 60fps - 40s.
